node.text:
“The name is Captain Carter!” 🇬🇧 So excited for my new Peggy Carter cosplay from What If…! It’s such a beautiful design ….Although the fact that the Union Jack is asymmetrical made my perfectionist brain break 😂 The breastplate is definitely my favorite part - it is heat formed worbla with foam on top. Also I love the little leather pouches I made. They’re so cute!
*
*
Gorgeous 📸 set by @thegeekstrong / @geekstrong 
*
Cosplay pieces made or modified by me!
Peggy wig from the talented @timeaftertimedesigns ❤️
*
*
#captaincarter #captainbritain #peggycarter #whatif #disneyplus #hayleyatwell ##captainamerica #cosplay #marvel #worbla #foam
